# ── Throwaway devnet keypairs — NEVER commit a key ───────────────────────────
# The program-identity keypair + the deploy/upgrade authority live here. declare_id!
# is the frozen on-chain identity; if these are lost, regenerate (see program/README).
program/.deploy-keys/
**/*-keypair.json
*-keypair.json
**/keys/

# ── Anchor / Solana build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────
.anchor/
target/
**/target/
# Isolated target dir for the mainnet-oracle build (surfpool_rehearse.sh) — never collides
# with target/ (the devnet build the Mollusk suite loads).
target-mainnet/
**/target-mainnet/
**/*.rs.bk
test-ledger/
.surfpool/

# Compiled SBF program binaries (rebuilt via `cargo build-sbf` / `anchor build`)
*.so

# ── Python (backend/, added by other lanes) ──────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.pytest_cache/

# ── Secrets ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
!.env.example

# ── JS / Anchor test deps ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
.yarn/
yarn-error.log

# ── Editor / OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
*.swp

# Internal design/business docs + dev probes — not part of the public submission
/ARCHITECTURE.md
/AgentForge_Markets_Business_Model_and_PRD.md
backend/scripts/probe_privy.py
backend/scripts/probe_txoracle.py
**/.venv/
.deploy-keys/
